OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773151901
OL,3,CPolice name murder victim as
OL,4,Cdetectives given more time to question
OL,5,Csuspect
OL,7,FA woman murdered in Enniskillen on
OL,8,FSaturday has been named by police as
OL,9,FEllie Flanagan.
OL,11,FThe 23-year-old was found dead in the
OL,12,FCorban Avenue area by police
OL,13,Finvestigating a car crash on the Carn
OL,14,FRoad near Tempo at about 9.15pm on
OL,15,FSaturday.
OL,17,FPolice arrested a man (45) on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of murder and other
OL,19,Foffences. They have been granted an
OL,20,Fextra 36 hours to question him.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
