OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773151901
OL,3,CPolice name murder victim as
OL,4,Cdetectives given more time to question
OL,5,Csuspect
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Gary
OL,8,FRobinson said: "Our thoughts are
OL,9,Ffirmly with Ellie's family and loved
OL,10,Fones at this very distressing time.
OL,12,F"Our team continues to work at pace to
OL,13,Festablish the circumstances
OL,14,Fsurrounding Ellie's death and to
OL,15,Fdetermine exactly what happened.
OL,26,@pD@POUtD@AOU
