OL,3,CPolice name murder victim as
OL,4,Cdetectives given more time to question
OL,5,Csuspect
OL,7,F"I would reiterate our appeal to
OL,8,Fanyone who may have information that
OL,9,Fcould assist us, to contact police on
OL,10,F101, quoting reference number 1564 07/
OL,11,F03/26. Any detail, no matter how
OL,12,Fsmall, could prove crucial to our
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,15,F"We urge anyone who was travelling on
OL,16,Fthe Cornagrade Road into Corban Avenue
OL,17,Fbetween 6.30pm and 10.45pm on Saturday
OL,18,Fevening and noticed anything out of
OL,19,Fthe ordinary, or suspicious, to make
OL,20,Fcontact with us.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
